{"tid":1631980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Repost]如果星期一晚18區開花失敗 就代表香港默許左呢條惡法","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:20:53.000Z","uid":47659,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9673a13043e1bc8a17c502ea3a9d7f9a374439c5","tid":1631980,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因為第日市面會如常運作</span><br />\n大家星期五講到有幾嬲有幾難接受 原來到上班日馬照跑舞照跳既?<br />\ncarrie仲有咩好驚呀?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">10月7號 18區啊</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WhZ52Us.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWhZ52Us.jpg&h=bae549ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">18區呀<br />\n18區呀</span></span><br />\n罷工文宣啊<br />\n行動Post呀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求下大家打返一場靚既三罷 起碼要8.5既級數先</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AsuebxZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAsuebxZ.png&h=344e2c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n深水埗：南昌V walk／楓樹街遊樂場／長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n荃灣：沙咀道遊樂場／荃灣公園<br />\n葵芳：葵廣／林士德足球場／林金殿外<br />\n青衣：青衣城／<br />\n觀塘：apm／觀塘遊樂場／<br />\n黃大仙：黃大仙中心／黃大仙廣場／摩士公園<br />\n油尖旺：朗豪坊／麥花臣球場／<br />\n紅土黃何九：馬頭圍邨球場／亞皆老街球場／<br />\n將軍澳：黨鐵Popcorn／香港單車公園／<br />\n沙田：新城市廣場／車公廟站 曾大屋遊樂場<br />\n馬鞍山：新港城／鞍誠街花園／<br />\n大埔：大埔超級城／大埔中央廣場／<br />\n上水： 上水廣場／彩園廣場<br />\n屯門：屯門市廣場／屯門政府合署／新和里球場<br />\n天水圍：嘉湖銀座／天耀<br />\n元朗：Yoho／大馬路<br />\n銅鑼灣：紀利佐治街／東角道<br />\n太古：太古城中心／鰂魚涌公園／<br />\n柴小杏：柴灣橋／柴灣公園<br />\n西區：中山公園<br />\n南區：香港仔中心／<br />\n東涌：東薈城噴水池／富東商場</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港時代革命<br />\n蒙面無罪惡法無理</span>"},{"pid":"8412f2bb6e82b4a08259869595acc1ecfc1b0998","tid":1631980,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cc868c99231dc44f6141fa850fda98ae316e500","tid":1631980,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85da98171a93ea70a5a6bdb9c2e86f0870e54fa2","tid":1631980,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:21.000Z","msg":"[Repost]如果星期一晚18區開花失敗 就代表香港默許左呢條惡法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631980</a>"},{"pid":"02b02540a0b569862a5c8799da004ff5ecdc6d63","tid":1631980,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:44.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"9353ab5a4666d2a3ca4f7fc3400a3f641cc6b979","tid":1631980,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:54.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"cab25578bc61dcc65228eac21a040d57bb80b87c","tid":1631980,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:49:45.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"99b41d1caf0c54d21fcba8ef5d0c81e74e1b1965","tid":1631980,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:49:55.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"7a677c798eae0979503a7e233a246ea9ba1c4563","tid":1631980,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85da98171a93ea70a5a6bdb9c2e86f0870e54fa2","tid":1631980,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:21.000Z","msg":"[Repost]如果星期一晚18區開花失敗 就代表香港默許左呢條惡法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631980</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:51:07.000Z","